detect thoughts
Level-2nd
CastingTime-1Action
Range/Area-Self
School-Divination
Attack/Save-WIS
OtherInfo-                For the duration, you can read the thoughts of certain creatures. When you cast the sell and as your action on each turn until the sell ends, you can focus your mind on any one creature that you can see within 30 feet of you. If the creature you choose has an Intelligence of 3 or lower or doesn't seak any language, the creature is unaffected.
